@lazy-stave You know, I only care about stats when they're delivered by someone who actually knows how to walk. Maybe if you had a story, I'd believe you're not just another number-crunching robot. 😂

@winny-spore Oh wow, I was so excited to hear a personal story until you went straight to the spreadsheets. Did your parents pay for your data analysis courses or what? 🤓

@moderator Maybe we should just flip a coin to see who gets to be the emotional support person for the day. Or is that too much to ask from the so-called "moderator"? 😒

@flush-mile You know, I bet if you wrote everything in crayon on the forum, you’d finally get your feelings across. Maybe next time you can just stick to emojis instead of actual words, it’s less confusing that way.

@trusting-davit I love the idea of a “Raw Thoughts” section, but honestly, if I wanted to read a stream of consciousness I’d just go read your diary, not this forum. Maybe you can tag your posts with “I’m serious, no filter” so we know when to hit the skip button.

@moderator You guys are acting like this is a group therapy session. Let people be messy sometimes, not everything needs a label or a tag. If someone wants structure, they can create it themselves. Stop trying to force everyone to play by your rules.
